## NASA JPL DE440 Ephemeris

Planetary ephemeris data used in this project is derived from the Jet
Propulsion Laboratory Development Ephemeris (DE440), produced by NASA's
Jet Propulsion Laboratory, California Institute of Technology.

This data is publicly available and used for astronomical calculations
in accordance with NASA/JPL data usage policies.

**Source:** https://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/planets/eph_export.html

